{"id":290728,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/04/维权网-三千余名上访维权人士到各部信访办抗议/","date":"2013-04-26T17:16:00Z","modified":"2013-04-26T17:16:00Z","title":"维权网 | 三千余名上访维权人士到各部信访办抗议（图）","content":"<p><div dir=\"ltr\"></p>\n<div></div>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" name='more'></a></p>\n<div><span>（维权网信息员唐韵报道）</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">4</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">26</span><span>日</span><span>是上访维权人士的公民维权日，来自全国各地的三千余位维权访民把国务院信访办、全国人大信访办和中纪委信访办（被上访人称为三骗胡同）围得水泄不通。不少便衣混进访民当中实施时时监控。二十多辆警车停在马路两侧，十多辆大公交车随时准备把维权访民送往久敬庄。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>据了解，现场有近两千名上海维权访民。上访维权人士表示，如果是下午</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">1</span><span>点</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">30</span><span>分以前进到“三骗”胡同里面，就很难自由的走出来，特别是上海，有专车等候着将上海的上访维权人士送往久敬庄。在现场，有十多名各地的蒙冤警察也前来参加维权活动。由于怕被抓回当地失去人身自由，还有很多访民远远的站在一边观望。在信访办里外不时发生冲突，众多的上访维权者被强行押上大公交车往久敬庄送。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>在抗议的现场，大家感受最深的就是没有人权和维权难。几年、十几年、甚至几十年的信访登记就是不解决问题。赶上各种敏感时期，还要被“稳控”无法登记，维权日来登记又被抓，被送往久敬庄黑监狱。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>大家希望，执政者能够真正做到依法行政，依法办案，真正做到让权力在阳光下运行。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span><br /></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-yqarcSRu4l4/UXqZ9oAVtyI/AAAAAAAAg88/clwpmgt_emw/s1600/2013-04-26+13.40.29.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"240\" src=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-yqarcSRu4l4/UXqZ9oAVtyI/AAAAAAAAg88/clwpmgt_emw/s320/2013-04-26+13.40.29.jpg\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-cFsNxZB83rw/UXqaAcrhosI/AAAAAAAAg9M/wO9qzgCgC2o/s1600/2013-04-26+13.48.49.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"213\" src=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-cFsNxZB83rw/UXqaAcrhosI/AAAAAAAAg9M/wO9qzgCgC2o/s320/2013-04-26+13.48.49.jpg\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-sRKu2653-ZI/UXqZ8wTfM9I/AAAAAAAAg80/QJoROKHFoO4/s1600/2013-04-26+13.40.10.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"240\" src=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-sRKu2653-ZI/UXqZ8wTfM9I/AAAAAAAAg80/QJoROKHFoO4/s320/2013-04-26+13.40.10.jpg\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-JCrZ4QOkmjE/UXqZ-ciSnsI/AAAAAAAAg9E/_-IfVAXyQvs/s1600/2013-04-26+13.43.35.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"240\" src=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-JCrZ4QOkmjE/UXqZ-ciSnsI/AAAAAAAAg9E/_-IfVAXyQvs/s320/2013-04-26+13.43.35.jpg\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<div></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-xA0_klVBLvI/UXqaAn5WYqI/AAAAAAAAg9Q/ITE_gvhnWmM/s1600/2013-04-26+14.15.06-1.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"149\" src=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-xA0_klVBLvI/UXqaAn5WYqI/AAAAAAAAg9Q/ITE_gvhnWmM/s320/2013-04-26+14.15.06-1.jpg\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<div><span><br /></span></div>\n</div>\n</p>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.us4.list-manage.com/subscribe/post?u=17daa75df533f6c6ff72e51ab&#038;id=b4fd4ae247\">\n<a href=\"http://eepurl.com/mstlf\">墙外新闻实时更新 欢迎订阅数字时代</a><br />\n <br /><input type=\"email\" value=\"\" name=\"EMAIL\" id=\"mce-EMAIL_in_post\" size=\"25\" style=\"display:block;\" placeholder=\"请输入您的邮件地址\" required><br />\n\t<input type=\"submit\" value=\"点击订阅\" name=\"subscribe\" style=\"height: 20px;\" id=\"in_post_subscribe\"><br />\n</form>\n","author":997,"categories":[18270,18269,20534],"tags":[16910,19196]}